<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٠٦٧ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ , عَنِ الْحَسَنِ ,<span class="c5"> فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{فَهَلْ مِنْ مُدَّكِرِ}</span> <span class="c4">[القمر: ١٥]</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«فَهَلْ مِنْ خَائِفٍ يَتَذَكَّرُ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>